PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776024347
OL,3,CPolls open in Hungary in an election
OL,4,Cthat could unseat populist Orban.
OL,6,FCasting her ballot in Budapest early
OL,7,FSunday, retiree Eszter Szatmari, 62,
OL,8,Fsaid she felt the election was
OL,9,F"basically our last chance to see
OL,10,Fanything vaguely resembling ...
OL,11,Fdemocracy in Hungary.
OL,13,F"We all have to make real effort to
OL,14,Fshow to the world that we are not what
OL,15,Fpeople thought we were in the past ten
OL,16,Fyears," she said.
OL,26,@lD@_rpoD@]rpqD@AOUxD@GO]
