OL,3,CPolls open in Hungary in an election
OL,4,Cthat could unseat populist Orban.
OL,6,FAfter the first hour of voting, 3.46%
OL,7,Fof registered voters had cast a
OL,8,Fballot, according to the National
OL,9,FElection Office. The figure was a
OL,10,Frecord in Hungary's post-Socialist
OL,11,Fhistory and nearly twice the turnout
OL,12,Ffrom the same period in the 2022
OL,13,Felections.
OL,26,@lD@_rp
