PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776024347
OL,3,CPolls open in Hungary in an election
OL,4,Cthat could unseat populist Orban.
OL,6,FThe biggest threat to Orban's time in
OL,7,Foffice is Peter Magyar, leader of the
OL,8,Fcentre-right opposition party Tisza.
OL,9,FThe 45-year-old is leading in
OL,10,Findependent polls, campaigned on
OL,11,Fissues affecting ordinary voters,
OL,12,Fincluding Hungary's faltering public
OL,13,Fhealth care and transportation
OL,14,Fsectors, and what he describes as
OL,15,Frampant government corruption.
OL,26,@lD@_rpnD@Zrp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
