OL,3,CPolls open in Hungary in an election
OL,4,Cthat could unseat populist Orban.
OL,6,FTisza won 30% of the vote in European
OL,7,FParliament elections in 2024, and
OL,8,FMagyar took a seat as an EU lawmaker.
OL,9,FTisza is a member of the European
OL,10,FPeople's Party, the mainstream, centre-
OL,11,Fright political family with 12
OL,12,Fnational leaders in the EU.
