PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776024347
OL,3,CPolls open in Hungary in an election
OL,4,Cthat could unseat populist Orban.
OL,6,FAdditionally, hundreds of thousands of
OL,7,Fethnic Hungarians in neighbouring
OL,8,Fcountries have the right to vote in
OL,9,FHungarian elections and traditionally
OL,10,Fhave voted overwhelmingly for Orban's
OL,11,Fparty.
OL,13,FThere have also been comments ahead of
OL,14,Fthe election that external meddling
OL,15,Fand internal fraud could taint the
OL,16,Fresult. Fidesz and Tisza both have
OL,17,Flaunched platforms for reporting
OL,18,Firregularities, accusing their
OL,19,Fopponents of planning to commit
OL,20,Felection abuses.
OL,26,@lD@_rprD@brp
